                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                <date>Decr. 4, 5610</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">My dear friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Perhaps I ought to have<lb/> replied ere this to your form received\n                the day before<lb/> I left <placeName>New York</placeName>, but I have deferred\n                until now<lb/> answering your letter in hopes of having something<lb/> to say that\n                might interest you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The Box sent by Express to me in <placeName>N York</placeName><lb/>\n                gave me a great deal of bother &amp; trouble, indeed<lb/> if it had not so happened\n                that my brother <persName>Alexr</persName><lb/> intended to see me off, it would not\n                have come<lb/> to or with me. I must say I felt somewhat put out<lb/> at receiving\n                your letter stating that you would<lb/> send it, after my particular &amp; respected\n                requests to<lb/> you to ship it with other things direct from<lb/> your city. The\n                bother of this box received as it was<lb/> on the day of my departure caused me to\n                miss<lb/> the company of my dear Parents, during the last<lb/> half hour of my stay\n                in their city, after their<lb/> taking the trouble &amp; undergoing the fatigue of\n                coming<lb/> down to the vessel.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It was recd too late to bring as freight &amp; therefore<lb/> I had\n                to watch it with my baggage all the way to <placeName>NO</placeName>,\n                particularly<lb/> when the <placeName>California</placeName> boys were hauling &amp;\n                dragging their baggage</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3gt5g225/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
