          "annotations": [
            {
              "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3gt5g225/canvas/p4/annopage",
              "type": "AnnotationPage",
              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3gt5g225/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">The <persName>revd Mr Raphael</persName> seems to be making\n                quite<lb/> a stir in your part of the country, and indeed<lb/> many of us here are\n                very anxious to hear &amp; see<lb/> him. I think he will not regret his visit\n                to<lb/> the <placeName>US</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am still kept pretty busy with finishing<lb/> the Synagogue &amp;\n                attending to the duties of my office<lb/> as President Heb. Benevolent Association\n                &amp; shall be happy<lb/> when some aspiring gentleman will take charge of<lb/>\n                these matters &amp; relieve me. In good earth I have<lb/> served long enough &amp;\n                now only see the glimmerings<lb/> of some little satisfaction.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It pains me to think that <persName>Mr Wm F's</persName> health<lb/>\n                will not permit his leaving home. What do you candidly<lb/> think of his situation\n                entre-vous. My dear little Aunt<lb/> is quite better (stronger) I hear; will you\n                give my love<lb/> to them both. I presume you see them as often as<lb/> when we used\n                so pleasantly to meet beneath their<lb/> hospitable roof.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Knowing that you feel interested in my<lb/> welfare I name having\n                gone into my old business as a h<add>?</add><lb/> I am happy to say that I am doing\n                very fairly indeed.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Let me hear from you my dear friend when<lb/> convenience &amp; the\n                humor may permit. How is your<lb/> health I trust better than heretofore.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">This ought to reach you in “<date>Hanuca</date>” may<lb/> you enjoy\n                the festival in health &amp; contentment</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">prays yours always the same</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Gershom K</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3gt5g225/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
            }
